"""Test for validate_existing_masking_view, false."""
new_masking_view_details = self.utils.get_masking_view(self.data.smis_mv_1)
element_dict = self.utils.compile_new_element_names(self.data.smis_mv_1,
    self.data.m_portgroup, self.data.m_initiatorgroup, self.data.smis_sg_1)
self.assertFalse(self.utils.validate_existing_masking_view(
    new_masking_view_details, self.data.m_portgroup, self.data.m_host_name,
    element_dict))
mock.patch.object(provisioning.ProvisioningFunctions, 'get_masking_view',
    return_value={'portGroupId': pcd.CommonData.m_portgroup, 'hostId': pcd.
    CommonData.m_host_name, 'storageGroupId': 'random_sg', 'maskingViewId':
    pcd.CommonData.rest_mv_1})
